I've got a laptop.
Annoyingly, it doesn't support suspend on close.
I can detect when the laptop gets closed, as a SMM interrupt kicks
in, and turns on the external monitor port, I can read this from the
video chip.
Before I reinvent the wheel, has anyone put something similar into X?
